title: Marketplace Roundtable #78: Sizing Up Bottom
description: We speak with Joseph L. Shaefer of The Investor's Edge (1:00 minute mark-32:30) and ANG Traders (32:30-56:00) about the current market environment, the effect of stimulus, and where the market might go in the coming months (this may not be the real sign we've turned a corner).
itunes:title: Sizing Up Bottom
itunes:author: Seeking Alpha
itunes:subtitle: We speak with two authors about the current state of the market and why there may be more room to go lower.
